137
00:06:45,414 --> 00:06:46,035
so that then you're.

138
00:06:46,969 --> 00:06:48,790
Again, you're sort of reminded, hey, it must be my turn.

139
00:06:48,850 --> 00:06:51,351
Realism is not our primary concern here.

140
00:06:51,471 --> 00:06:52,211
It's functionality.

141
00:06:53,792 --> 00:06:57,653
